flowchart TD
    A[Observe code risk] --> B[Classify force]
    B --> C{Behavior known?}
    C -- no --> D[Add characterization tests]
    C -- yes --> E[Select smallest refactor]
    D --> E
    E --> F[Transform one step]
    F --> G[Run verification]
    G --> H{Behavior preserved?}
    H -- no --> I[Revert or fix with evidence]
    I --> G
    H -- yes --> J{Target force addressed?}
    J -- no --> E
    J -- yes --> K[Record residual risk and cleanup trigger]
